.. rubric:: sql

- ``close_connection`` ‚Äî Explicitly close one or all cached database connections.

  > ``gway sql close-connection``

- ``execute`` ‚Äî Execute SQL code or a script resource. If both are given, run script first.

  > ``gway sql execute``

- ``infer_type`` ‚Äî (no description)

